<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>Two adjoining pieces of a <rs type="material">white marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">sarcophagus</rs> base, partially adapted with a view to re-use (<measure precision="circa" type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">1.92</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.28</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.83</measure>).</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> on the moulding, which was already faulty or damaged (the lettering in lines 2 and 3 dips into a chipped area).</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p>Second to third centuries A.D. standard forms; ll.1, 2, ave. <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.025</measure>; l.3, <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.03</measure>. Diacritical points on either side of the second Υ in l.3; ΜΗ ligatured, l.3.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p>
<date notBefore="0101" notAfter="0300" exact="none">Second to third centuries A.D.</date> (<rs type="criteria">lettering</rs>)
</p>
</div>
